org.sakaiproject.memory.impl

Class MemCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.memory.impl.MemCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer, org.sakaiproject.memory.api.Cache, org.sakaiproject.memory.api.Cacher
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericMultiRefCacheImpl, HardCache

    public class MemCache
extends Object
implements org.sakaiproject.memory.api.Cache, Observer

    A Cache of objects with keys with a limited lifespan.

    When the object expires, the cache calls upon a CacheRefresher to update the key's value. The update is done in a separate thread.
